There are growing concerns Google 's Waze application poses a danger to police because of its ability to track their locations .
The tech giant is now under pressure by top cops to turn off the traffic app 's police-tracking function .
The Waze app allows users to tag the locations of parked police vehicles , accidents , potholes and more .
Ismaaiyl Brinsley , 28 , killed two NYPD police officers in December .